   <div class="sosumi"> 
    <ul> 
     <li>1. iOS 7 required.</li> 
     <li>2. iOS 6 required.</li> 
     <li>3. iTunes Pass not available in Brazil, China, or Turkey.</li> 
    </ul> 
    <ul> 
     <li>iTunes Gift Cards, iTunes Gifts, and iTunes Pass can be used only in the country in which they are purchased. Requires iTunes account and prior acceptance of license and usage terms. Must be 13 or older. Compatible software, hardware, and Internet access required. Nonrefundable (except as required by law). No resale. Full terms apply, see <a href="http://www.apple.com/legal/itunes/us/gifts.html">apple.com/legal/itunes/us/gifts.html</a>. © 2014 Apple Inc.</li> 
